data.description: Welcome to the stunning 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home sitting on 1.08 acres in Trussville. Step inside from the covered porch to be greeted by hardwood floors that flow throughout the home. From the spacious kitchen, you'll enjoy an open concept floor plan which allows for easy entertaining and gathering. The living room is centered with a wood burning fireplace featuring stone detailing. The master bedroom features a walk in closet and newly renovated en suite bathroom which now has a new shower with tile, new sink and cabinet and marble countertop. Just down the hall you will find 2 additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. The hardwood floors in all 3 bedrooms were recently upgraded from carpet. Downstairs features a 2 car garage and basement with tons of additional space and storage. The deck provides the ideal space for relaxing. Just minutes from entertaining, shopping and food.
